race.description: Bet365 Same Race Multi 3Yo Mdn Plate
race.comment: COSTALOTTA (8) was safely held at the last run before a break but was close to a maiden success and has run well fresh. Drawn for a good run and expected to go close. KILCARN (10) was heavily backed on debut at Warrnambool and was fair but will be much improved. Freshened since and back to 1200m should see sharp improvement. CAROLINA ROSE (7) is a three-year-old filly by leading sire I Am Invincible out of Jamaican Rain. Jumping out well. Showing ability and off the low draw is worth keeping safe.  BIVTONIC (1) returns from a spell on the back of a jump-outs. Opened initial campaign with a fifth at Sale over 1100m. Improver with a senior aboard and expecting a positive return.
